exceptions.exn: In environment l, m, a, b : lb H : length l = length m H0 : forall l m a b : lb, length l = length m -> l ≂ m -> a ≂ b -> l ++ a ⪯ m ++ b Unable to unify "?M1455 ++ ?M1457 ⪯ ?M1456 ++ ?M1458" with "(l ++ a) ↓ (m ++ b) = l ↓ m ++ a ↓ b".

In environment H0 : forall l m a b : lb, length l = length m -> l ≂ m -> a ≂ b -> l ++ a ≂ m ++ b l, m, a, b : lb H : length l = length m H1 : forall x y : lb, x ≂ y -> forall x0 y0 : lb, x0 ≂ y0 -> x ↓ x0 ⪯ y ↓ y0 Unable to unify "?M1797 ↓ ?M1800 ⪯ ?M1798 ↓ ?M1801" with "(l ++ a) ↓ (m ++ b) = l ↓ m ++ a ↓ b".

In environment H2 : forall l m a b : lb, length l = length m -> l ≂ m -> a ≂ b -> l ++ a ≂ m ++ b H1 : Morphisms.Proper (lb_mask_equiv ==> lb_mask_equiv ==> lb_mask_equiv) lb_meet l, m, a, b : lb H : length l = length m Unable to unify "?M2190 ↓ ?M2191 = ?M2191 ↓ ?M2190" with "(l ++ a) ↓ (m ++ b) = l ↓ m ++ a ↓ b".

In environment H4 : forall l m a b : lb, length l = length m -> l ≂ m -> a ≂ b -> l ++ a ≂ m ++ b H3 : Morphisms.Proper (lb_mask_equiv ==> lb_mask_equiv ==> lb_mask_equiv) lb_meet H0 : forall l m : lb, l ↓ m = m ↓ l l, m, a, b : lb H : length l = length m Unable to unify "?M2652 ↓ ?M2653 = ?M2653 ↓ ?M2652" with "(l ++ a) ↓ (m ++ b) = l ↓ m ++ a ↓ b".

In environment H5 : forall l m a b : lb, length l = length m -> l ≂ m -> a ≂ b -> l ++ a ≂ m ++ b H2 : Morphisms.Proper (lb_mask_equiv ==> lb_mask_equiv ==> lb_mask_equiv) lb_meet H1 : forall l m : lb, l ↓ m = m ↓ l l, m, a, b : lb H : length l = length m Unable to unify "l ↓ m ++ a ↓ b" with "(l ++ a) ↓ (m ++ b)".

original: intro H. apply lb_mask_equiv_app. - auto. - apply lb_meet_eq_Proper. + apply lb_meet_comm. + apply lb_meet_comm. - reflexivity.
